ruleLogicalInfo.ruleDesc: Validate  the data integrity of the data present in CLM_LINE table against CLM table.

paramsVOLst.paramValue:
SELECT * 
FROM #PRM_EDW_DATABASE#.CLM_LINE
WHERE CLM_SOR_CD IN #PRM_CLM_SOR_CD#

 AND ((#PRM_INCR_FLAG# = '2'
 AND ( UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW#  OR LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# ))

OR(#PRM_INCR_FLAG# <> '2'AND ( UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW#
OR CRCTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_CRCTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# OR LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# ))) 

AND (CLM_ADJSTMNT_KEY)  NOT IN ( 
SELECT CLM_ADJSTMNT_KEY
FROM  #PRM_EDW_DATABASE_2#.CLM
WHERE CLM_SOR_CD IN #PRM_CLM_SOR_CD#)
